OL,6,FA former councillor who harassed his
OL,7,Fex-girlfriend and threatened to kill
OL,8,Fher cats has been sentenced.JMark
OL,9,FMewse, 64, used to work for Salisbury
OL,10,FCity Council and began his campaign of
OL,11,Fharassment after his relationship with
OL,12,Fthe victim ended.JHe started appearing
OL,13,Fat bus stops along the routes where
OL,14,Fshe worked as a bus driver.
OL,16,FHe also began delivering a barrage of
OL,17,Fcards, flowers and gifts - despite
OL,18,Fbeing told she was not interested in a
OL,19,Frelationship.JMewse even threatened to
OL,20,Fkill her cats before chasing after her
OL,21,Fwhen she threatened to call police.
