OL,6,FHe claimed the victim was lying about
OL,7,Fthe harassment because he didn't take
OL,8,Fher on a trip to New York.
OL,9,FProsecutors, along with the Crown
OL,10,FProsecution Service Wessex were able
OL,11,Fto disprove his version of events,
OL,12,Fpiecing together CCTV evidence and
OL,13,Fwitness testimonies, leading him to be
OL,14,Ffound guilty.
